mindmap
  root((Vaultword Password Manager))
    Project Goals
      Secure password storage
      Easy credential management
      Strong password generation
    Frontend Extension
      React popup interface
      Tabs
        Passwords Tab
        Add Tab
        Generator Tab
      Authentication Screens
        Registration
        Login
        Vault lock and unlock
      Local Features
        Client-side encryption and decryption
        Clipboard copy
        Search and filter
    Backend API
      Node.js and Express API server
      Routes
        Authentication routes
        Credential routes
      Middleware
        JWT authentication
      Validation and error handling
    Security Model
      AES-256-GCM for credentials
      Master-password-based protection
      JWT session authentication
      Password hashing for user accounts
      Recovery code reset flow
    Database Layer
      SQLite database
      Users table
      Credentials table
      Data access module
    Core Flows
      Account registration and login
      Save encrypted credential
      Retrieve and decrypt credential
      Update and delete credential
      Generate strong passwords
    Deployment and Execution
      Localhost API server
      Built Chrome extension from the dist folder
      Environment variables
        JWT_SECRET
        PORT
        DB_PATH
        ALLOWED_ORIGINS
